    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "System Timetable\nEffective June 11, 1998\nWE THINK OUR FREQUENT\nFLYER PROGRAM\nIS THE BEST\nIN THE INDUSTRY.\nAPPARENTLY, SO DO YOU.\nContinental's OnePass® frequent flyer\nprogram voted #1 by the people\nwho fly the most.\nContinental Airlines\nWork Hard.\nFly Right...",
      "For reservations call your\ntravel agent or\n1-800-523-FARE\n(1-800-523-3273)\nFor complete vacation packages\ncall Continental Airlines Vacations at\n1-800-634-5555\nFor automated flight\ninformation call\n1-800-784-4444\nAlways ask for an\n#TICKET\nPurchase tickets online at\nwww.flycontinental.com"
    ],
